'''Felix Kalu Nmecha''' (born 10 October 2000) is a [[Germany|German-born]] [[English people|English]] [[Association football|footballer]] of [[Nigerian people|Nigerian]] descent currently playing as a [[midfielder]] for [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]].
